Mod mobs
Vanilla mobs
Gelid (Frozen Zombie)
Murk (Sunken Skeleton)
Thicket (Jungle Zombie)
Verdant (Jungle Skeleton)
Stray
Husk
Bogged
Parched
Enable Gelid
Enable Gelid spawns
When enabled, gelid can spawn instead of zombie in cold biomes.
Spawn chance of Gelid
Spawn chance of gelid, for example 80% means that gelid will spawn in place of 80% of all zombies spawned in cold biomes.
Minimum Y level for Gelid spawns
Minimum Y level for gelid spawns, for example 62 means that gelid will spawn only above the ocean Y level.
Enable Gelid spawners in dungeons
When enabled, spawners in dungeons in cold biomes can be gelid spawners instead of zombie spawners.
Chance of Gelid spawner in dungeons
Chance of gelid spawner in dungeons, for example 80% means that gelid spawner will be in place of 80% of all zombie spawners in cold biomes.
Enable Gelid spawners in Trial Chambers
When enabled, spawners in trial chambers can be also gelid spawners.
